      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 Lexus RX 350, finished in a timeless Nebula Gray Pearl. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior paint retains a brilliant shine, with only minor, unavoidable stone chips on the front fascia that do not detract from its overall presence. Inside, the Parchment leather seating is remarkably clean and supple, showing very light wear on the driver\u2019s bolster and absolutely no punctures or stains. As a non-smoker's vehicle, the cabin smells fresh and inviting. All technological features\u2014including the navigation system, heated and ventilated seats, and the premium audio suite\u2014are fully functional. Under the hood, the 3.5L V6 engine runs smoothly and quietly, backed by a comprehensive service history from certified technicians. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains taut and responsive. With a set of Michelin tires that have significant tread remaining and a clean title in hand, this Lexus represents a reliable, high-quality choice for anyone seeking luxury without the new-car depreciation.",
